innerHtml: For Godot Wild Jam #80, my friend Keagan and I made a game called "Prof. Oddheart or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Elevator". After successfully completing two game jams prior to this, I thought it was time to finally tackle one as a team. I created a "How We Made" video that you can watch below or at the link above, which covers the journey in more depth.
